OVERVIEW

Introducing the charcoal grill perfected: the Char-Griller® Gravity Fed 980 Charcoal Grill in Blue. Get the unmatched flavor and versatility of charcoal in a fraction of the time. With over 980 square inches of cooking space, you can cook for the whole crew on this massive grill. Equipped with an LCD controller with Bluetooth and Wi-Fi connectivity, you can control the temperature of your grill and monitor your cook right from your phone. A slide damper and precision control fan keeps the smoke rolling and the fire going. Go from low and slow at 200 degrees to a quick and hot searing 700 degrees in 20 minutes. A triple walled hopper can hold 16 lbs. of briquette charcoal and a porcelain coated fire channel not only means more fuel efficiency, it also makes the grill last season after season.

  • Porcelain-Coated Cast Iron Cooking Grates

  • Folding Front Shelf

  • Fixed Side Shelf

  • Digital LCD Controller with Bluetooth and WiFi

  • Triple Walled Insulated Hopper

  • Insulated Barrel Lid

  • Built In Meat Probe

  • Precision Control Fan

  • Slide Damper
